.TH NUTRIENTS 1 "June 2026" "nutrients 0.1.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
nutrients \- track daily calories and macronutrients
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B nutrients
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B nutrients
opens a GTK 4 and Libadwaita nutrient tracker designed for narrow Linux
phone screens.
.PP
The application stores its local JSON data under
.IR $XDG_DATA_HOME/nutrient-tracker/data.json .
.SH FEATURES
The application supports editable daily goals, monthly summaries, Open Food
Facts searches, and optional camera-based barcode scanning.
